	<Title>
		Do you respect the mind-body connection?
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Feel stressed out? Try meditation and put the mind-body connection to work for you. During meditation, you focus your attention and eliminate the stream of jumbled thoughts that may be crowding your mind and causing stress. This process results in enhanced physical and emotional well-being.&lt;/p&gt;
